data.title: Duplicate rowIDs generated on INSERT to ACID transactional tables · Issue #8452 · trinodb/trino
data.meta_description: When we INSERT data into transactional table rowId counter is reset on each input page. As a result for any INSERT which processes significant number of rows we will end up with duplicate rowIDs in created file. Noticed by @electrum here...
